title: Having A Baby For Him
description: I arrived on college campus and bumped into Ethan Tiry. The arrogant prick, published photos of me on his website,´Pranks By Us´.I had a perfect GPA, I went to college to be sociable, meet new friends and for once in my life, party.Yet, I couldn’t. Ethan had me wrapped around his little finger.All of a sudden, my world became rocked, shaken and f**** stirred.
author: Foxy Tale
